DESCRIPTION:Join us on Saturday\, June 27\, from 1–3 PM at Whispering Vine Fourth St. for our annual Rosé Party—an afternoon dedicated to all things pink and sparkling!\nEnjoy tastings of 30+ Rosé and Sparkling Wines\, flatbreads\, and a chance to win in our raffle featuring bottles of rosé\, merch\, and more. Each guest will receive a raffle ticket upon check-in with their first glass.\nTickets: $50 per person (Includes all wine tastings\, flatbreads\, and raffle entry)\nEvent Details:\n- 30+ Rosé and Sparkling Wines\n- Flatbreads included\n- Raffle prizes: Rosé bottles\, merch\, and more\n- Pink attire encouraged\n- Limited to 70 tickets\nCelebrate the summer season in style—don’t miss out!
LOCATION:4201 W Fourth St Reno\, NV 89523
